headline: Do Visa’s New Sponsorships and AI Questions Subtly Shift the Long-Term Narrative For (V)?
summary: In recent weeks, Visa announced a multi-year renewal and expansion of its global partnership with Oracle Red Bull Racing and Visa Cash App Racing Bulls, continued broadening its payments footprint through deals such as the Banqup collaboration, raised several billion US dollars via new senior notes, and faced regulatory pushback on acquisitions alongside fresh political and AI-related scrutiny of its business model. Beyond headline sponsorships, these developments together highlight how Visa...
